    "en": {
      "title": "The Acting President goes to the military hospital to see the injured",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe visited the Army Hospital today to inquire about the well-being of the military personnel who were injured during the unrest that occurred on the 13th at Polduwa intersection near the Battaramulla Parliament entrance.",
        "There, the President also engaged in a cordial meeting with the military personnel.",
        "Army Commander and former Member of Parliament Mr. Ashu Marasinghe and others participated in this event."
      ],
